stx.functional.PartialFunction1<K, V>
Collection<Map<K, V>, stx.Tuple2<K, V>>
A cross-platform, immutable map with support for arbitrary keys. TODO: Use an array of lists to avoid unnecessary copying when adding/removing elements.
